explain select id, headline, category
from vector_ivfflat_include_phase7_include
order by l2_distance(embedding, "[1,2,3]")
limit 2 by rank with option 'mode=force';
TP QUERY PLAN
Project
  ->  Sort
        Sort Key: l2_distance(vector_ivfflat_include_phase7_include.embedding, ) INTERNAL, vector_ivfflat_include_phase7_include.id INTERNAL
        Limit: 2
        ->  Table Scan on vector_ivfflat_include_phase7.vector_ivfflat_include_phase7_include
